<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='10964:10973'>　毛詩注疏卷九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='10995:11022'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0004', 'WYG', '009-19a' );" name="009-19a" class="pb">[009-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='11022:11033'>　毛詩注疏卷九考證</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='11033:11056'>魏風園有桃章園有桃箋食園桃而已○李樗曰園桃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='11056:11080'>　非終歲常食之物鄭說不足取當從毛𫝊以園桃起</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='11080:11086'>　興為安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='11086:11101'>不知我者○唐石經作不我知者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='11101:11124'>陟岵章夙夜無已上愼旃哉○無魯詩作毋上魯詩作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='11124:11128'>　尚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='11128:11145'>伐檀章河水清且漣猗○猗魯詩作兮</span><br/>
